name: Experiment Or Die #114
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. The pace of the NFT space and the ambitions of this project have started to get the best of me juuuust a little bit. I ache for more sleep and am constantly angling for more time for this and that, it definitely feels like a maelstrom that no matter how much you fight back you'll never escape that pull that you feel. That pull to create, that pull to say yes, that pull to try and make everyone proud, that pull to be successful...that pull to leave a lasting mark on the world. You can't escape it so why not lean in? Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
